query:
/*+ NoMergeJoin(l o) NoHashJoin(l o s) NoMergeJoin(l o s n) */ select n.n_name,
sum(l.l_extendedprice * 1 - l.l_discount) AS revenue
from lineitem AS l
inner join orders AS o
on l.l_orderkey = o.o_orderkey AND o.o_orderdate >= '1993-01-01'::date AND o.o_orderdate < '1993-01-01'::date + '1'::interval(4)
inner join supplier AS s
on l.l_suppkey = s.s_suppkey
inner join nation AS n
on s.s_nationkey = n.n_nationkey
inner join region AS r
on n.n_regionkey = r.r_regionkey AND r.r_name = 'AMERICA'
inner join customer AS c
on c.c_custkey = o.o_custkey AND c.c_nationkey = s.s_nationkey group by n.n_name order by revenue desc;
